solution:
The line $y=\frac x2$ will intersect the two vertical sides of the square, as shown below:
[asy]
real f(real x)
{

return x/2;
}

import graph;
size(6cm);
real a = 8;
pair A=(-a,a), B=(a,a), C=(a,-a), D=(-a,-a);
draw(A--B--C--D--cycle);
