solution:
Let $O$ be the origin.  Then we can express the area of triangle $ABC$ as
\[[ABC] = [ABO] + [BCO] - [ACO].\][asy]
unitsize(1.5 cm);

pair A, B, C, O;

A = 2*dir(70);
B = 2*sqrt(3)*dir(40);
C = 3*dir(10);

draw(A--B--C--cycle);
draw(A--O);
draw(B--O);
draw(C--O);
